  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WordInfilter62
    This is the infilter for the Word by Word pipeline, which is discussed in the Filters for Document Processing guide.

    This is the outfilter for the Word by Word pipeline, which is discussed in the Filters for Document Processing guide.
    WordSpaceFixup62
    This is a fixup outfilter which is part of the Word by Word pipeline, which is discussed in the Filters for Document Processing guide.

Package com.deltaxml.pipe.filters.dx2.wbw.v62 Description

This package contains the versions of the Word by Word pipeline filter which were replaced in XML Compare 6.3. It is advised to move to the new versions of these filters (available in the com.deltaxml.pipe.filters.dx2.wbw package). See the release notes for the 6.3 release for more information.
